## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c4f51-102">下表显示当前支持的选项。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4f51-102">The following table shows the currently supported options.</span></span>  
  
|<span data-ttu-id="c4f51-103">类别</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4f51-103">Category</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="c4f51-104">设置</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4f51-104">Setting</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="c4f51-105">值/效果</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4f51-105">Value/effect</span></span>|  
|--------------|-------------|-------------------|  
|<span data-ttu-id="c4f51-106">Contract — 协定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4f51-106">contract</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="c4f51-107">继承</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4f51-107">inheritance</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="c4f51-108">如果打开协定继承，则为 `true`；如果关闭协定集成，则为 `false`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4f51-108">`true` to turn contract inheritance on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="c4f51-109">默认值为 `true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4f51-109">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="c4f51-110">Runtime — 运行时</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4f51-110">runtime</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="c4f51-111">检查</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4f51-111">checking</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="c4f51-112">如果打开运行时检查，则为 `true`；如果关闭运行时检查，则为 `false`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4f51-112">`true` to turn run-time checking on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c4f51-113">默认值为 `true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4f51-113">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c4f51-114">您可使用此特性，如以下示例所示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4f51-114">You can use this attribute as illustrated in the following examples.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c4f51-115">关闭对整个程序集的运行时检查：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4f51-115">To turn off run-time checking for the entire assembly:</span></span>  
  
```  
[assembly:ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c4f51-116">打开对特定类型的运行时协定检查：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4f51-116">To turn run-time contract checking on for a specific type:</span></span>  
  
```  
   [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", true)]  
   class TypeWithRuntimeChecking {  
  
       ...  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c4f51-117">打开对特定方法的运行时检查：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4f51-117">To turn run-time checking off for a specific method:</span></span>  
  
```  
// Turn off all contract inheritance from interface IList<T>  
[ContractOption("contract", "inheritance", false)]  
class MyConcurrentList<T> : IList<T> {  
   ...  
}  
  
[ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
public override MyMethod(int x) {  
   // no inherited contracts checked at runtime,  
   // no invariants checked at runtime.  
   ...  
}  
  
       [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
       public void MethodWithoutRuntimeChecking(...) {  
          ...  
       }  
   }  
  
```
